 	video bank is changed.  Dispatch the `int_rasterdraw()' alarm if
 	pending.
	(set_video_mode): Update `idle_data_ptr'.

	* c64/vicii.c (int_rasterfetch): New, cleaner algorithm.  It also
 	couple of bugs in the old one.

